          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The following parameters provide processor core performance-level information. First, determine the number of types of processor cores with ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "hw.nperflevels",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ". Then, for each of the parameters, replace ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "N",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": " with a number between ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "0",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " and the number of performance levels minus one. Lower values of ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "N",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text": " indicate higher-performance core types.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
